{"tid":1531640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正式宣佈］醫院開始出現文革式批鬥","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T13:30:53.000Z","uid":311420,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"96350fd3d42fd49966a0888c83e0792f62bbbd6b","tid":1531640,"uid":311420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"P牌仔第一次開po ，講野1999，sor <br />\n<br />\n話說今日醫護響應三罷，係醫院發起靜坐抗議，以黑口罩，黑絲帶為記，罷工不罷醫。<br />\n但返工時，同個平時幾好傾既大叔病人打招呼，卻換來佢大聲指住個黑口罩鬧我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大叔：哦，原來你係黑衫果班人<br />\n我：無論我地咩立場政見，都係本住良知同專業去醫人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n病人唔理解，算，但好快又有d支那大媽同事叫我除口黑色口罩，話咁樣好核突。<br />\n<br />\n我聽到火都黎，乜撚野核突？夠你地班人核突？淨係帶黑口罩，扣黑絲帶，貼下pepe打氣貼紙係制服都睇唔過眼，咁你地同班藍絲撕紙狗連一張紙都容不下有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最悲哀既係，竟然有同事怕表態而唔敢戴黑口罩，我想講，你已成功中左白色恐怖既圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來今時今日，帶黑口罩都需要勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我委屈係個心度，忍唔住想打上黎分享下<br />\n但一唸起為我地犧牲既義士，被人話兩句有咩所謂</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e4e871cde379e1028cb63a0779da529b62fd9419","tid":1531640,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54c5b80185b86a1d20cc07f3a6f5ba6377b0d72","tid":1531640,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6548cfb4a730363accc0c57f7651481c686851b","tid":1531640,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"佢地咁撚勁, 咁咪唔好醫囉"},{"pid":"0881b0dd2961b81214cbcefde8d8cb4233c1add1","tid":1531640,"uid":45934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:47:44.000Z","msg":"對住呢d patient 做返basic 就夠"},{"pid":"9bb0e592f6360c5ae0622ddeb57aee889e215dbb","tid":1531640,"uid":283551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:48:17.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬你地 u r not alone"},{"pid":"fa4e5fe026a67ff811ecf655c55921f65433c8fa","tid":1531640,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:48:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔中意有事唔好去醫院囉</span>"},{"pid":"4255874d5de6265f9adc38f392f3732993655d00","tid":1531640,"uid":112355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"香港啲醫院係咁嫁喇<br />\n唔鐘意嘅返大陸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016bdbc7e8202cbc7bfc5a85a3e163490a1f4fd4","tid":1531640,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e6548cfb4a730363accc0c57f7651481c686851b","tid":1531640,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"佢地咁撚勁, 咁咪唔好醫囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:48:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/SIG=3q7l60r/qqo0006qspoo1sns012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D3q7l60r%2Fqqo0006qspoo1sns012.jpg&h=45c6fa6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你永遠都滿足唔到所有人<br />\n你只可以做你覺得做得岩既事情<br />\n人地唔明, 人地唔了解係佢問題"},{"pid":"e9a2551a0f1b970e5b30f7d6c0d16bc6c137fe22","tid":1531640,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:48:54.000Z","msg":"手足頂住<br />\n你地既行動真係好需要勇氣"},{"pid":"cd7f555738df84b77c6d923931aab231be27f32c","tid":1531640,"uid":169953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"如果認為政見重要過醫生既尊業判斷<br />\n咁咪自行出院<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535d08ea29589fb936995497a65dc569f9c98eb5","tid":1531640,"uid":311420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6548cfb4a730363accc0c57f7651481c686851b","tid":1531640,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"佢地咁撚勁, 咁咪唔好醫囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:49:36.000Z","msg":"返大灣區睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a3085f3a644113e054739ce2fbc6445075d021","tid":1531640,"uid":287449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借位宣傳<br />\n侵侵同d外國人都冇加你fb同ig，點知你想要咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再係facebook同ig自己圍爐打飛機啦，一齊黎開始國際戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個tweet幾秒鐘，一蚊都唔洗，又唔洗綁電話，安全又快捷，快d一齊轉用twitter啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">twitter文宣共識TG</span>： </span></strong><a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR2x1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=ad616c9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n內有twitter詳細教學，開個account唔洗3分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文唔好驚比人笑？唔洗驚，國際文宣谷幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🔥<span styl